Title: Nicky Larson et le parfum de Cupidon
Writer: Julien Arruti (adaptation), Julien Arruti (dialogue), Julien Arruti (screenplay), Pierre Dudan (adaptation), Pierre Dudan (dialogue), Pierre Dudan (screenplay), Tsukasa Hôjô (manga "City Hunter"), Philippe Lacheau (adaptation), Philippe Lacheau (dialogue), Philippe Lacheau (screenplay), Pierre Lacheau (adaptation), Pierre Lacheau (dialogue), Pierre Lacheau (screenplay)
Actors: Philippe Lacheau, Élodie Fontan, Tarek Boudali, Julien Arruti
Plot: Nicky Larson, the best private investigator in the business, is called for a high-risk mission: to recover the perfume of Cupid, a perfume that would make irresistible the one who uses it.
